summary:
...AIR FORCE HURRICANE HUNTERS FIND HELENE A MAJOR HURRICANE...
 As of 2:25 PM EDT Thu Sep 26
 the center of Helene was located near 26.7, -84.9
 with movement NNE at 16 mph.
 The minimum central pressure was 959 mb
 with maximum sustained winds of about 120 mph.
